## Description {#details}

A key and value pair.

While not technically a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/yaml/node">Node</a> under the YAML representation graph, it is easier to treat them this way.

TODO: Consider making this not a child of <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/yaml/node">Node</a>.
